"text":"“Come on!” the sailors said to each other. “Let’s cast lots. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jos 7:14–18","book":"Jos","chapter":7,"verse":14,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Sm 10:20","book":"1Sa","chapter":10,"verse":20,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Sm 14:41–42","book":"1Sa","chapter":14,"verse":41,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Pr 16:33","book":"Pro","chapter":16,"verse":33,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ac 1:23–26","book":"Act","chapter":1,"verse":23,"letter":"e"},{"kind":"text","text":" Then we’ll know who is to blame for this trouble we’re in.” So they cast lots, and the lot singled out Jonah. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Nm 32:23","book":"Num","chapter":32,"verse":23,"letter":"f"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Pr 16:33","book":"Pro","chapter":16,"verse":33,"letter":"g"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Jos 7:14–18","book":"Jos","chapter":7,"verse":14},{"label":"1Sm 10:20","book":"1Sa","chapter":10,"verse":20},{"label":"1Sm 14:41–42","book":"1Sa","chapter":14,"verse":41},{"label":"Pr 16:33","book":"Pro","chapter":16,"verse":33},{"label":"Ac 1:23–26","book":"Act","chapter":1,"verse":23},{"label":"Nm 32:23","book":"Num","chapter":32,"verse":23},{"label":"Pr 16:33","book":"Pro","chapter":16,"verse":33}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Jon:1:8","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Then they said to him, “Tell us who is to blame for this trouble we’re in. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jos 7:19","book":"Jos","chapter":7,"verse":19,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Sm 14:43","book":"1Sa","chapter":14,"verse":43,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"text","text":" What is your business, "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Gn 47:3","book":"Gen","chapter":47,"verse":3,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Sm 30:13","book":"1Sa","chapter":30,"verse":13,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"text","text":" and where are you from? What is your country, and what people are you from?”"}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Jos 7